TITLE: Internal Message Handling in KvQueue Listener
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how KvQueue internally handles incoming messages and routes them to the appropriate callbacks.
SOURCE: https://github.com/savory/docs/blob/main/src/techniques/kvQueue.md#2025-04-19_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
this.kv.listenQueue((msg: QueueEvent) => {
			const type = msg.type;
			const callback = this.listenersMap.get(type);
			if (callback) {
				return callback(msg.data);
			}
			throw Error('Unhandled message type');
		});
```

